body:
Theres so much contradiction in Lol lore, (even in champs that haven&#039;t been affected by lore changes yet.)

for example a quote by Wolf (Kindred):
&quot;they stick in my claws&quot; 
like seriously... what claws? he&#039;s a disembodied head...

And Aurelion Sol:
&quot;Stars are **not** born,  they are made, by me.&quot;
&quot;I grieve for every star never born.&quot;
So are stars born?.. or made? please pick one, it doesn&#039;t bode well when even the same champ has contradiction in quotes..
Also by him:
&quot;There are no dragons like me.&quot;
&quot;Celestial dragons live and die by **our** own rules.&quot;
So.. are there more celestial dragons? or is he the only one? again... pick one..

lets try keep everything consistent haha :p
